<strong>Studio Album, released in 2002</strong><br><br>

<strong>Songs / Tracks Listing</strong>
<p style="padding-left:5px;">1. And By The Water (4:45) <br>2. Paradise Square (13:42) <br>3. Striking Out A Single Note For Love (11:08) <br>4. Fly In A Bottle (5:48) <br>5. Darkfall (2:35) <br>6. White Glove (15:26) <br>7. Aftermath (10:02)<br><br>Total Time: 63:26</p>

<strong>Line-up / Musicians</strong>
<p style="padding-left:5px;">- Daniel Fäldt / vocals, sitar<br>- Jonas Hallberg /  guitars, backing vocals<br>- Stefan Renström / bass, keyboards, voice<br>- Mattias Jarlhed / drums, percussion<br><br>Note: The actual instrumentation could not be fully confirmed at this moment<br></p>

<strong>Releases information</strong>
<p style="padding-left:5px;">
CD Galileo Records &#8206;- GR 007  (2002, Switzerland)<br>
</p>


